Nitpick: on point 10)<p><pre><code>  cause issues down the lime.
</code></pre>
&quot;lime&quot; is a typo, should be &quot;line&quot;

The methodology used excludes a number of services using SparkPost. For e.g. the excerpt below of an Intercom header. It&#x27;s a challenging problem to solve given the complexity of email delivery and appreciate this was a fun project to take on.<p>Return-Path: &lt;bounces+XXXX@XXXX.intercom-mail.com&gt;
